deck: Secret Wars Collected Comics
description:
Marvel UK were already reprinting the Secret Wars saga, in their 80-issue weekly. This special collects the first two issues of the US series (or the first three issues of the UK series, depending on which one you were following).

Confusingly, this comic is called 'Secret Wars Special', but it also carries the 'Collected Comics' branding used by Marvel UK for their other reprint specials (Transformers, Thundercats etc).
name: Secret Wars Collected Comics
